Preconditions:
- The weights array must not be null.
- The days value must be greater than or equal to 1.
- The weights array must have at least one element.
- The weights array must not contain any negative values.
- The weights array must not contain any values greater than 500.

Postconditions:
- The returned ship capacity must be the minimum capacity required to ship all the packages within the given number of days.
- The order of the packages on the conveyor belt must be maintained.
- The ship must be loaded with packages in the order given by the weights array.
- The ship must not be loaded with more weight than its maximum weight capacity.
- All the packages on the conveyor belt must be shipped within the given number of days.